high_descs: Turn left for two steps, turn right for three steps and stop at the counter.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife behind the green bottle on the counter.
Turn around for one step, take a left for four steps and turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the knife in the white coffee mug on the top shelf, with the blade facing down.
Take the mug out of the fridge, with the knife still in it and shut the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Put the mug on the counter, in the same place as the blade of the silver knife, but to the right, a few inches from the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup from the refrigerator with a knife in it on the counter by the stove.

high_descs: Walk forward to the counter.
Pick up the knife from behind the wine bottle.
Turn right and walk to the door then turn left and look up to face the freezer.
Open the freezer and put the knife in the coffee cup.
Take the coffee cup from the freezer and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Put the coffee cup on the counter to the left of the silver knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold coffee cup with a knife inside on the counter next to the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the oven, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the door, turn left again to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the large metal knife in the white mug that is on the top shelf.
Pick up the white mug with the large metal knife in it and close the fridge.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Put the white mug with the large metal knife in it on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a white mug with a large metal knife in it on the counter.
